  3. Uncomment the aggregate-indices node in pipeline.xml
  4. Update documentBasePath below to match where your document pages live
     (e.g. "/" + page.lang + "/seals" or "/" + page.lang + "/inscriptions")
#}
---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Persons
---

